18 (c) The Board of Trustees shall grant an accidental disability retirement
19 allowance to a member of the Law Enforcement Officers’ Pension System if:
20 (1) the member is totally and permanently incapacitated for duty arising
21 out of or in the course of the actual performance of duty without willful negligence by the
22 member; and
23 (2) the medical board certifies that:
